  "comment": "Zelos LED Tube RGBW in/outdoor use: The Zelos Tube revolutionizes your lighting setup with its advanced features and versatile design. Offering full RGBW (CW+WW) colour mixing capabilities, the Zelos Tube puts complete control in your hands, allowing you to craft the perfect ambiance for any setting. Each tube can be independently controlled, enabling effortless creation of intricate lighting arrangements with minimal effort. Built for versatility, the Zelos Tube boasts a lightweight and durable design, making it ideal for both on-the-go shoots and studio productions. Explore a diverse range of special effects to elevate your projects—from commercials to musical performances—with stunning visual effects that captivate and inspire.",
